org.cytoscape.model
Interface CyProject

public interface CyProject

CyProject is the top level of the Cytoscape model hierarchy. A CyProject maintains a list of all of the networks associated with this project, the information about how each project was created, and a list of logs and other information related to data provenance. Roughly, a CyProject is equivilent to a Cytoscape session.
